  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nThis happens in both prater and mainnet: we have a lot of topic peers\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1250\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-12-28 at 10 48 00\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/147525988-bd3e0ccc-d271-4c43-9c6b-6717ede07624.png\">\r\n\r\nbut so few mesh peers\r\n<img width=\"1290\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-12-28 at 10 49 48\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/147526074-a87c7d01-c45b-4d01-8724-1324e06bd975.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n+ Given `options.D = 8`, we should have up to 8 mesh peers per subnet\r\n+ Track both mesh peers (already exist) and topic peers in the grafana dashboard\r\n",
